query:
SELECT DISTINCT t.component, t.componentType, COUNT(*) as count
FROM tmlReadings t
JOIN inspections i ON t.inspectionId = i.id
WHERE i.vesselTagNumber = '54-11-067'
GROUP BY t.component, t.componentType;
